{"tid":1439231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史自己改寫] 反擊影音組及諜報戰計劃 求鍵盤戰士及義士及忍者","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:25:14.000Z","uid":151057,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5bcfccb49f855606a4d75e0a9f46a3c162cf10eb","tid":1439231,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>影音組</ins></strong>是製作民記用影片 其成果為<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104265217595123/videos/464610360783769/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104265217595123%2Fvideos%2F464610360783769%2F&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68sxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=f41cd897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104265217595123/videos/464610360783769/</a><br />\n<strong><ins>Data組</ins></strong>任務為整理資料 包括<br />\n(1)成立資料庫 負責紀錄所有警察罪行 以防資料被流失<br />\n(2)整理政府每場記招主張 供諜報組及影音組使用<br />\n-<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次革命演變成長期抗爭<br />\n亦都會係香港最後一代抗爭!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">決定勝敗</span>方既就會係諜報戰<br />\n君可以見到政府出奇地一個開足三個記者會正是因為<br />\n想要龐大政府資源 鋪天蓋地式用諜報戰打敗我地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>諜報組</ins></strong>需要大量人手分別為<br />\n諜報分析 諜報擴散 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>諜報分析</ins></strong>所做既工作係針對唔同界別 唔同利益既人<br />\n搵出佢地所在意既地方同埋佢地既思考邏輯<br />\n再去發佈針對性相對資訊<br />\n因為你永遠唔可以同隻牛講雞肉幾好味<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0UyeZKh_Dl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0UyeZKh_Dl0&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68sxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e970c1d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0UyeZKh_Dl0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qyfQoQwEliw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqyfQoQwEliw&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68sxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=a91f6b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qyfQoQwEliw</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>諜報擴散</ins></strong>所做既工作正正係忍者既工作<br />\n潛入對面敵陣 將諜報分析製作既用佢地果種圈子既邏輯同埋行動方式<br />\n出奇不意咁不停推銷<br />\n<br />\n諜報戰既成本係講到可以過億元<br />\n不單是大數據亦要天價廣告投放<br />\n我地並唔擁有咁龐大既資源<br />\n我地唯一擁有就係人既決心<br />\n<br />\n諜報戰需要大量人手!!!!<br />\n請立刻入總GP地址 同大家講你願意幫手 我地會安排!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JABufk663ySWkJVdQrwKtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJABufk663ySWkJVdQrwKtQ&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68sxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=721dda41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JABufk663ySWkJVdQrwKtQ</a><br />\n<br />\n最後請記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">&ldquo;雖然抗爭時間久了，<br />\n但絕對不能忘記，<br />\n我們一直以來的理念，<br />\n一定要堅持下去。&rdquo;</span>"},{"pid":"b1ddcc2c27f1c92173afea290399456c674f1629","tid":1439231,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6cbf1d4129915d109400c638fcad9d6cf02beaf3","tid":1439231,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bce180bfb3f740cfb1004042618f24aa7692cf9","tid":1439231,"uid":293841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"之前寫咗篇 睇下有冇用<br />\n<br />\n心理學碩士獻計 ：文宣如何打心理戰？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33803d4b701c90d307288b8919571b1eb431a79a","tid":1439231,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"99d4bdd3784e5a9f9b6e40c119c74b3dab3fa77c","tid":1439231,"uid":37982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65ad439d95de066f5a7b8e4df619d682d2bacaf3","tid":1439231,"uid":37982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c574103e4663f648a4ac34b2438b38ee83396e4","tid":1439231,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9118d3beb5ca8cedc50dc79c11972ae0c1331b1","tid":1439231,"uid":293841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5aaf66bc09d59723082b941205a165eb0c8e85d","tid":1439231,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71fef8d10db1b8b435a9d9541a710672fca82f86","tid":1439231,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bce180bfb3f740cfb1004042618f24aa7692cf9","tid":1439231,"uid":293841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"之前寫咗篇 睇下有冇用<br />\n<br />\n心理學碩士獻計 ：文宣如何打心理戰？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:03:25.000